{"tha-ap377:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap377:0.2":"Bodhivandanavagga ","tha-ap377:0.3":"Sattapanniyattheraapadana ","tha-ap377:1.1":"“Sumano nama sambuddho, ","tha-ap377:1.2":"uppajji lokanayako; ","tha-ap377:1.3":"Pasannacitto sumano, ","tha-ap377:1.4":"sattapannimapujayim. ","tha-ap377:2.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap377:2.2":"Sattapannimapujayim; ","tha-ap377:2.3":"Duggatim nabhijanami, ","tha-ap377:2.4":"Sattapannipujayidam phalam. ","tha-ap377:3.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap377:3.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap377:3.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap377:4.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap377:4.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap377:4.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap377:5.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap377:5.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap377:5.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap377:6.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma sattapanniyo thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap377:7.1":"Sattapanniyattherassapadanam pancamam. "}